## handoff
- produced: complete Vite+React worship playback app; 3 songs; 6-stem Web Audio synthesis; mixer, transport, waveform, section nav, A/B loop, count-in, cue cards; built and deployed to portfolio demos dir
- decisions: 3 songs (added Holy Ground in E/76bpm) to push richness-10; ROOT_HZ updated with E:82.4; all synthesis uses existing researcher spec params; no em-dashes in user-visible text
- next needs: deploy step to push michaelwegter.com to GitHub Pages (git commit + push main); verify live URL https://michaelwegter.com/demos/audio-software-engineer-needed-for/ returns 200
- risks: iOS Safari AudioContext requires user gesture (handled in engine._ensureContext() via resume + first-interaction); OfflineAudioContext render of 6 stems for song 3 (190s loops = ~25s each buffer at 44100) may take 2-3s on slow machines (loading overlay covers this)
